        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "When Ben-hadad heard this message, as he was drinking with the kings in the temporary shelters, he said to his servants, “Station yourselves.” So they stationed themselves against the city."
